\c 17
\s Zvigumbuso nokukangamwirana
\p
\v 1 Zvino wakati kuvadzidzi: Hazvingaitiki kuti zvigumbuso zvisavuya. Asi vurombo \add kune\add* wazvinovuya naye.
\v 2 Zvaiva nani kwaari kuti guyo riremberedzwe pamutsipa wake, akandirwe mugungwa, pakuti agumbuse mumwe wavaduku ava.
\v 3 Muzvichenjerere: kana hama yako ikakutadzira, umudzore; kana akatendevuka, umukangamwire.
\v 4 Kunyange akutadzira kanomwe pazuva, akadzokerazve kwauri kanomwe, achiti: Ndatendevuka; umukangamwire.
\s Simba rokutenda. Varanda pasina
\p
\v 5 Zvino vapositora vakati kunaShe: Tiwedzerei kutenda kwedu.
\v 6 Ishe akati: Kana maiva nokutenda kwakaita setsanga yemasitadha, maiti kumuhabhurosi: Dzurwa, usimwe mugungwa, uchakuteererai.
\v 7 Asi ndiani kwamuri ungava nomuranda unorima, kana unofudza mombe, akati kwaari, achibva kumunda: Vuya, ugare pakudya.
\v 8 Handiti ungadoti kwaari: Ndigadzirire zvandingadya, uzvisunge chivuno, undipakurire, kusvikira ini ndadya, ndikamwa; mushure iwe ugozodya, nokumwa?
\v 9 Ko ungatenda muranda, zvaaita zvakanga zvarairwa here? Handifungi.
\v 10 Saizvozvo nemwivo, kana maita zvose zvamarairwa, muti: Tiri varanda pasina, takaita sezvataifanira kuita.
\s Jesu unoporesa vanamaperembudzi vanegumi
\p
\p
\v 11 Zvino wakati achienda Jerusarema, akapfuvura napaSamaria neGariri.
\v 12 Zvino wakati achipinda munomumwe musha, akasongana navarume vanegumi vaiva namaperembudzi, vamire kure.
\v 13 Vakasimudza manzwi, vachiti: Jesu, Tenzi, tinzwirei ngoni!
\v 14 Zvino wakati achi\add va\add*vona, akati kwavari: Endai mundozviratidza kuvaprista, Vakati vachienda, vakapora.
\v 15 Zvino mumwe wavo, wakati avona kuti ndaporeswa, akadzoka, achikudza Mwari nenzwi guru;
\v 16 ndokuwira pasi nechiso patsoka dzake, akamuvonga. Zvino iye wakanga ari muSamaria.
\v 17 Ipapo Jesu akapindura akati: Havana kuporeswa vanegumi here? Vapfumbamwe varipiko?
\v 18 Hapana kuwanikwa wadzokera kuzokudza Mwari, asi uyu mutorwa.
\v 19 Ipapo akati kwaari: Simuka, uende; kutenda kwako kwakuponesa.
\s Vushe bwaMwari, nokudzoka kwaShe
\p
\v 20 Zvino wakati achibvunzwa navaFarisi kuti vushe bwaMwari bwunosvika rinhi, akapindura, akati: Vushe bwaMwari habwuvuyi bwuchivonekwa.
\v 21 Vuye havangati: Tarirai pano, Kana: Tarira uko. Nokuti tarirai, vushe bwaMwari bwuri mukati menyu.
\v 22 Akati kuvadzidzi vake: Mazuva achasvika amuchatsvaka kuvona rimwe ramazuva oMwanakomana womunhu, asi hamunga\add ri\add*voni.
\v 23 Vachati kwamuri: Tarirai pano! Tarirai uko! Regai kuenda, kana kutevera;
\v 24 nokuti semheni inopenya, ichibva kunorumwe \add rutivi\add* pasi pedenga ichivhenekera kusvikira kunorumwe \add rutivi\add* pasi pedenga, ndizvo zvichaita Mwanakomana womunhuvo nezuva rake.
\v 25 Asi unofanira kumbotambudzika zvizhinji, nokurashwa nezera iri.
\v 26 Zvino sezvazvakanga zvakaita namazuva aNowa, ndizvo zvazvichaitavo namazuva omwanakomana womunhu.
\v 27 Vaidya, vaimwa vaiwana, vachiwaniswa, kusvikira zuva rakapinda Nowa muareka, mapopoma akasvika, akaparadza vose.
\v 28 Sezvazvakanga zvakaitavo namazuva aRoti; vaidya, vaimwa, vaitenga, vaitengesa, vaisima, vachivaka;
\v 29 asi nomusi wakabuda Roti muSodoma, kwakanaya moto nesarufa. Zvichibva kudenga, zvika\add va\add*paradza vose.
\v 30 Ndizvo zvazvichaitavo nezuva iro, Mwanakomana womunhu raachavoneswa naro.
\v 31 Nezuva iro, unenge ari pamusoro peimba, nhumbi dzake dziri mumba, ngaarege kuburuka kundodzitora; saizvozvovo, uri kumunda ngaarege kudzokera shure.
\v 32 Rangarirai mukadzi waRoti.
\v 33 Aninani unotsvaka kuponesa vupenyu bwake, ucharashikirwa nabwo, vuye aninani unorashikirwa nabwo, uchabwuchengetedza.
\v 34 Ndinoti kwamuri: Vusiku ubwo vaviri vachava panhovo imwe, mumwe uchatorwa, mumwe uchasiyiwa.
\v 35 Vaviri vachakuya pamwe chete, mumwe uchatorwa, mumwe uchasiyiwa.
\v 36 Vaviri vachava kumunda; mumwe uchatorwa, mumwe uchasiyiwa.
\v 37 Ipapo vakapindura, vakati, kwaari: Kupiko Ishe? Akati kwavari: Apo panomutumbi, ndipo panovunganira magora.
